    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Fast ‚Ä¢ Safe ‚Ä¢ Secure</span>
          <h1 class="title">Prescription delivery by drone ‚Äî <span style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--accent-2));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent">from pharmacy to doorstep</span>.</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">AltitudeX is building an on‚Äëdemand service to deliver critical medicines directly to patients. Designed by an aerospace engineering student team, with a focus on reliability, safety, and delightful user experience.</p>
          <div class="badges">
            <div class="badge">2 kg target payload</div>
            <div class="badge">VTOL biplane concept</div>
            <div class="badge">Secure delivery code on landing</div>
            <div class="badge">Patient‚Äëfirst design</div>
          </div>
          <div class="actions">
            <a href="#join" class="cta">Request early access</a>
            <a href="#tech" class="ghost">See the tech</a>
          </div>
          <p class="note">Prototype milestone: aiming for a public demo by <strong>September 2025</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="drone">
          <img alt="Concept visual of AltitudeX VTOL biplane drone" src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='900' height='560'><defs><linearGradient id='g' x1='0' x2='1'><stop offset='0' stop-color='%234da3ff'/><stop offset='1' stop-color='%237d6bff'/></linearGradient></defs><rect width='100%' height='100%' fill='%2310161f'/><g fill='none' stroke='url(%23g)' stroke-width='2' opacity='0.9'><path d='M60 320 C 200 200, 700 200, 840 320'/><path d='M60 340 C 200 220, 700 220, 840 340'/><path d='M60 360 C 200 240, 700 240, 840 360'/></g><g fill='none' stroke='%23cfe3ff' stroke-width='3'><rect x='360' y='250' width='180' height='60' rx='6'/><line x1='290' y1='280' x2='360' y2='280'/><line x1='540' y1='280' x2='610' y2='280'/><line x1='260' y1='230' x2='640' y2='230'/><line x1='260' y1='330' x2='640' y2='330'/><circle cx='260' cy='230' r='26'/><circle cx='640' cy='230' r='26'/><circle cx='260' cy='330' r='26'/><circle cx='640' cy='330' r='26'/></g><text x='50%' y='86%' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' fill='%23a8b4c7' font-family='system-ui' font-size='18'>VTOL biplane concept illustration</text></svg>" />
          <p class="note">Illustration for concept only.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section id="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why AltitudeX</h2>
        <p class="lead">Built for time‚Äëcritical prescriptions and routine refills alike, with safety and patient privacy at the core.</p>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>End‚Äëto‚ÄëEnd Chain of Custody</h3>
            <p>Pharmacy‚Äësealed payloads are logged at handoff and tracked until delivery, with tamper‚Äëevident packaging and live telemetry.</p>
            <span class="chip">‚úî <span>Traceable</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Secure Handoff Code</h3>
            <p>On landing, the drone displays a one‚Äëtime code. The recipient enters the matching code in their app (or keypad) to release the parcel.</p>
            <span class="chip">üîê <span>Two‚Äëfactor drop</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Fast & Efficient</h3>
            <p>VTOL for precise urban takeoff/landing, fixed‚Äëwing for range efficiency ‚Äî the best of both worlds for real deliveries.</p>
            <span class="chip">‚ö° <span>Rapid dispatch</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Cold‚ÄëChain Ready</h3>
            <p>Sensors in the payload bay log temperature and shock, with alerts if thresholds are exceeded.</p>
            <span class="chip">üå°Ô∏è <span>Monitored</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Safety‚ÄëFirst</h3>
            <p>Geofencing, automated return‚Äëto‚Äëhome, health checks before every sortie, and layered failsafes.</p>
            <span class="chip">üõ° <span>Redundant</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Privacy by Design</h3>
            <p>Minimal data collection, strong encryption, and clear consent flows for patients and partners.</p>
            <span class="chip">üîè <span>GDPR‚Äëminded</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section id="how">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <p class="lead">From prescription to your doorstep in four simple steps.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step"><h3>1. Request</h3><p>Patient places an order via the AltitudeX app or through a partner pharmacy‚Äôs portal.</p></div>
          <div class="step"><h3>2. Prepare</h3><p>Pharmacy verifies the prescription, seals the parcel, and hands off to an AltitudeX operator.</p></div>
          <div class="step"><h3>3. Fly</h3><p>Drone departs vertically, transitions to forward flight, and navigates via pre‚Äëapproved corridors.</p></div>
          <div class="step"><h3>4. Handoff</h3><p>On landing, the app displays a one‚Äëtime code. Enter it to unlock and collect. Done.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tech -->
    <section id="tech">
      <div class="container split">
        <div>
          <h2>The vehicle</h2>
          <p class="lead">A long‚Äërange VTOL biplane glider concept with quad lift motors and a pusher for cruise.</p>
          <div class="grid-3" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)">
            <div class="card"><h3>Payload</h3><p>Target 2 kg with modular payload bay options (standard, cold‚Äëchain).</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Propulsion</h3><p>Four vertical motors for takeoff/landing; one forward motor for efficient cruise.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Airframe</h3><p>Lightweight foam‚Äëcore with composite reinforcement for stiffness and durability.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Avionics</h3><p>Redundant IMU, GNSS, health monitoring, and controlled transition logic.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Safety & compliance</h2>
          <p class="lead">Designed to align with UK CAA guidance for unmanned aircraft operations. We will only operate within granted permissions and approved test areas.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Pre‚Äëflight self‚Äëchecks and mission simulation</li>
            <li>Geofencing and dynamic no‚Äëfly updates</li>
            <li>Return‚Äëto‚Äëhome & controlled descent modes</li>
            <li>Observer‚Äëassisted flights during trials; BVLOS only where permitted</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="note">Note: Final specs and procedures may evolve during testing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- For partners -->
    <section id="partners">
      <div class="container split">
        <div>
          <h2>For Pharmacies & Clinics</h2>
          <p class="lead">Delight patients and reduce delivery friction.</p>
          <div class="card"><h3>Simple onboarding</h3><p>Start with manual dispatch; upgrade to API integration for automatic job creation and status webhooks.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>Chain‚Äëof‚Äëcustody dashboard</h3><p>Live mission tracking, proof‚Äëof‚Äëdelivery with code entry, and environmental logs.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>Service areas</h3><p>We‚Äôll expand gradually with pilot sites near partner locations to ensure quality and compliance.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>For Patients</h2>
          <div class="card"><h3>Clear, easy app</h3><p>Request deliveries, set safe landing spots, and manage prescriptions. No jargon.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>Secure pickup</h3><p>Enter the one‚Äëtime code shown on the drone‚Äôs panel (or within the app) to release the parcel.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>Support that cares</h3><p>Chat and phone support during operating hours. Accessibility‚Äëminded flows.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Join -->
    <section id="join">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-panel">
          <div>
            <h2>Join the pilot program</h2>
            <p class="lead">We‚Äôre selecting pharmacies and early users for our first trials. Tell us a little about you.</p>
            <form id="earlyAccessForm" onsubmit="return submitForm(event)">
              <div class="grid-3" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr">
                <div>
                  <label for="name" style="display:block;margin:0 0 6px;color:var(--muted)">Name</label>
                  <input id="name" name="name" placeholder="Jane Doe" required />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="email" style="display:block;margin:0 0 6px;color:var(--muted)">Email</label>
                  <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="role" style="display:block;margin:0 0 6px;color:var(--muted)">I am a‚Ä¶</label>
                  <input id="role" name="role" placeholder="Patient / Pharmacist / Clinic" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="margin:12px 0 10px">
                <label for="msg" style="display:block;margin:0 0 6px;color:var(--muted)">Anything else?</label>
