      <div class="container">
        <h2>FAQs</h2>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <details class="card"><summary>Where do you operate?</summary><p>We‚Äôll begin with limited pilot zones in partnership with local pharmacies, then expand as approvals allow.</p></details>
          <details class="card"><summary>Is it safe?</summary><p>Safety leads every decision: geofencing, return‚Äëto‚Äëhome, health monitoring, and cautious expansion of operations.</p></details>
          <details class="card"><summary>What about bad weather?</summary><p>Operations pause in unsafe conditions. Patients will receive updates and rescheduling options.</p></details>
          <details class="card"><summary>How is privacy handled?</summary><p>We collect only what‚Äôs necessary to deliver your order, encrypt data in transit and at rest, and give you control over your data.</p></details>
          <details class="card"><summary>Do you integrate with pharmacy systems?</summary><p>Yes. Start manually, then integrate via API/webhooks for automated dispatch and status updates.</p></details>
          <details class="card"><summary>Can I help?</summary><p>Absolutely. Join the pilot program or reach out if you‚Äôre an engineer, pharmacist, or community partner.</p></details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <div class="brand"><div class="logo">X</div><span>AltitudeX</span></div>
      <div>
        <span>Contact: </span><a href="mailto:hello@altitudex.example">hello@altitudex.example</a>
        <span class="note" style="display:block;margin-top:6px">¬© <span id="year"></span> AltitudeX. All rights reserved.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    // Smooth scroll for internal links
    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(a=>{
      a.addEventListener('click',e=>{
        const id=a.getAttribute('href').slice(1);
        const el=document.getElementById(id);
        if(el){ e.preventDefault(); el.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'}); }
      });
    });

    // Simple form handler (demo only)
    function submitForm(e){
      e.preventDefault();
      const form=e.target;
      const name=form.name.value.trim();
      const email=form.email.value.trim();
      const role=form.role.value.trim();
      const msg=form.msg.value.trim();
      const out=document.getElementById('formMsg');
      if(!name||!email){ out.textContent='Please fill your name and email.'; out.style.color='var(--warn)'; return false; }
      const payload={name,email,role,msg,ts:new Date().toISOString()};
      console.log('Early access request:',payload);
      out.textContent='Thanks! Your request has been noted. We\'ll be in touch.';
      out.style.color='var(--ok)';
      form.reset();
      return false;
    }

    // Year in footer
    document.getElementById('year').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
